Pre-assessment Data Workshop

This years data workshop will be held virtually. A joint workshop focusing on copper rockfish, black rockfish, and canary rockfish is scheduled for Tuesday January 31 from 9 a.m. until 3 p.m. and Wednesday February 1st from 9 a.m. to 12 p.m. Information to connect to the meeting can be found online.
